    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Poor-condition car that is best viewed as a project, parts candidate, or very budget-minded driver. It shows significant cosmetic wear, an aged overall presentation, and the kind of mechanical and interior needs you should expect from a car in this state. Buyers should plan on repairs, sorting, and deferred maintenance, but for someone looking for an inexpensive starting point, it could still have some usable value.",
