      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle is a solid opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer who wants dependable basics without stretching the budget. It shows its age and will best suit someone comfortable with a well-used vehicle, but it still offers real value as an inexpensive commuter, backup car, or starter project. If you\u2019re looking for low-cost entry into ownership with honest potential, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 7495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for affordable wheels without the big price tag? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great project to tinker with. It\u2019s being sold honestly as a well-used vehicle, and for the right buyer it offers a lot of value for the money. If you want something straightforward, inexpensive, and ready for its next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable drivetrain. Starts up, moves out well, and has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it easy to own and straightforward to sort. Not a show car, but it has honest driver potential, good road manners, and the bones of a capable, usable vehicle for someone who wants affordable transportation with upside. Priced to reflect condition while still leaving room for the next owner to add value.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, runs, gets the job done. Rough around the edges but priced to move fast. Solid budget beater.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Honest, affordable, and full of scrappy charm, this car is the kind of ride that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s a straightforward set of wheels for someone who values function, character, and the freedom of an inexpensive entry point. Whether you need a basic commuter, a first car to learn on, or a hands-on project with personality, this one offers a chance to get on the road without stretching the budget. A little rough around the edges, sure\u2014but that\u2019s part of its appeal: dependable old-school grit and plenty of potential for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to serve, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a practical buyer who values function over flash, but it presents as an honest car with solid everyday potential. A smart opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive wheels without overpaying.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    }
